data.text:
Apt 78 (4447 Broadway) is having an all-out Women’s Appreciation Day bash tomorrow. The one and only DJ Jazzy Joyce will be on the wheels of steel. Our good friend Ami V will there doing her nail art thing, free make-up and oh yeah, open bar from 8 to 10 pm courtesy of Qreme. What more could you ask for?

We invite you to like our Facebook page and follow us on Twitter, or e-mail us at [email protected].
